{
  "stem": "3988.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a couple weeks-- I don't remember how long-- they called me up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and they offered me a job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I worked for Dodge, you know, for a while, I don't know, a year, two years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I didn't care for, you know, factory work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I want to learn a trade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't have nothing-- you know, and learned a trade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the same thing, my aunt had another brother, which was in the glass business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'll try to be a plumber, electrician, anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But-- So I told my boss in the factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, well, I'm going away for a couple weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, I said I have family in California or someplace.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't tell him I was looking for another job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they go-- so I took off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I figure for in case I don't like it, you know, I can always go back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I see it, learned the trade, I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's better than work in the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, you know, I worked in the factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it happened too in the factory, they had an incident with lots of Polish people worked in that factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because it was a Polish town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Hamtramck, you know, is like a-- lots of Polish population.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when I worked there, they didn't know I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "All those Polish people, they thought, you know, I'm a Polack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I talk to them in Polish, you know, and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then we came-- Jewish holidays, like Rosh Hashanah, Yom Kippur, I told my boss, you know, I'm not working tomorrow because it's the holiday.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the next day after holidays, I came to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
